        "subject": "LU-6325 ptlrpc: remove ptlrpcd_use_cpts tunable",
        "message": "LU-6325 ptlrpc: remove ptlrpcd_use_cpts tunable\n\nThe ptlrpcd_use_cpts tunable was included in the original code change\nfor CPT-aware ptlrpcd threads to allow for an easy fallback to the\nold behavior. Remove the tunable and related code.\n\nThis change builds on\n  I3ac40ea56f9c792c3e7c36967e2e1f20105c566c\n  I38c5e40cdefc8c22ca697239004342c4c36a58ad\n\nTested-by: Stephen Champion <schamp@sgi.com>\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Weber <olaf@sgi.com>\nChange-Id: If4496c947a53e8b1547f8fde221889040b3a63fd\n"
